No. 11-6614. Tommy Alexander, Sr., Petitioner v. United States. 565 U.S. 1009, 132 S. Ct. 536,

181 L. Ed. 2d 389,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 7745. October 31, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied. Justice Kagan took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 429 Fed. Appx. 404.
